videos.headline: Lynx hold off Mercury to advance to WNBA semifinals
videos.description: After Odyssey Sims sinks a bucket to extend the Lynx's lead, Skylar Diggins-Smith scores to cut into the lead, but is unable to hit the winning shot as time expires, giving Minnesota an 80-79 win over Phoenix.
